      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPACE ACADEMY (2) brings strong numbers to this contest and the top metro hoop rides. Has been cruelled by wide gates but draws kinder today. Went close four back at Belmont and missed a nose from the back at York before the latest. On a quick back-up and is the one to beat. STARTLING STAR (1) also brings form from stronger and needed the first-up outing at Pinjarra. The step up to 1600m suits her and she missed a lip at Belmont at the trip at her lone second-up outing. Fitter and go close. SIDE SHOW (6) had excuses last time but was good over this distance at Ascot prior and is well in the mix. HOT CHATTER (8) has the inside barrier and won't be far away. HENRY HAS SPOKEN (3) will be fitter and looks next best.",
